text:
Good job, Natsuha.
You seemed really enthusiastic during today's lesson!

Hehe,
did it appear that way from your perspective as well?

I felt like I've been
in high gear all day today.

Could it be that I'm being influenced by the shared
living situation without even realizing it...?
Haha, that might be the case!

Especially with members from outside of Houkura
joining us this time, everything feels even fresher.

Yeah. But make sure not to overdo it, okay?
I trust you, Natsuha, but...

Thank you.
I won't push myself beyond my limits, of course.

Well then, break's over.
Let's give it our all for one more push!

Got it.
I'm rooting for you, Natsuha!
